=Print Interview=

Philippe Van Parijs is Professor of Economic and Social Ethics at the Université Catholique de Louvain. His books include Marxism Recycled (1993) and Real Freedom for All (1995). This interview originally appeared in Imprints vol. 1 no. 3 ,  in March 1997. The interview was conducted by Christopher Bertram.


